  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Iraq: Strengthening and Defending Union Partnerships</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Solidarity Center provides workshops to teach workers about their rights under the new labor law in Iraq, and trains union leaders and activists on the role of trade unions in advocating for the enforcement of those laws. The Solidarity Center also provides occupational health and safety training for workers in the construction sector and assists in documenting and reporting worker rights violations.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Solidarity Center strengthens Iraqi trade unions&#x2019; capacity to ensure the protection of worker rights&#x2014;such as decent wages, safe working conditions and freedom of association&#x2014;in accordance with Iraq&#x2019;s new labor and trade union laws.</narrative>
  </description>
